---
import Base from "@layouts/Base.astro";
import CompanyCultureSection from "@layouts/components/CompanyCultureSection.astro";
---

<Base showFooter={true}>
  <section class="team-and-careers-page py-5 pt-[96px] pb-[96px]">
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center my-5">
      <div class="w-1/2">
        <h1 class="text-white text-center">Embark on a Career That</h1>
        <h1 class="text-center text-[#9d95fa]">Redefines Industries</h1>
        <p class="text-white text-center px-4">
          Join ABC Ventures and be a part of a team that’s driving innovation
          and transforming the future of startups worldwide.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pb-3 container">
      <div class="w-full flex flex-wrap images-card">
        <img class="w-1/2 p-2" src="/images/content-gallery-1-1024x417.jpg" />
        <img class="w-1/4 p-2" src="/images/content-gallery-2.jpg" />
        <img class="w-1/4 p-2" src="/images/content-gallery-3.jpg" />
        <img class="w-1/4 p-2" src="/images/content-gallery-4.jpg" />
        <img class="w-1/2 p-2" src="/images/content-gallery-5-1024x417.jpg" />
        <img class="w-1/4 p-2" src="/images/content-gallery-6.jpg" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="p-4 my-5 border-b container lg:py-24 border-b-purple-300/50">
    <div class="grid grid-rows grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
      <div class="px-4">
        <h2 class="my-0 text-[3rem] font-semibold text-black-900">
          Why Choose

          <span class="block text-[#9d95fa]">ABC Ventures?</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="px-4 text-[#6b7280] text-base font-medium">
        <p class="mb-[1.2rem]">
          At ABC Ventures, we don’t just offer jobs; we offer career-defining
          opportunities. Here, you’ll be immersed in an environment that values
          innovation, fosters growth, and encourages every team member to push
          the boundaries of what’s possible. Being part of our team means more
          than working for a leading venture capital firm; it means being at the
          heart of progress, working alongside industry experts, and
          contributing to projects that leave a lasting impact.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-8 mx-auto alignfull lg:py-24">
    <div class="container">
      <div>
        <h1 class="my-0 text-gray-90 font-medium">
          Our Impact <span class="text-[#9d95fa]">by Numbers</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-[60px] mt-[10px] font-medium">
          Here’s a glimpse of the tangible impact our team has made:
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap">
        <div class="w-1/4 p-4">
          <h3 class="text-[#776bff] font-semibold">
            20+ <span class="text-[#b5aeff]">Startups Funded</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#6b7280] mt-5">
            Investing in the future, one startup at a time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/4 p-4">
          <h3 class="text-[#776bff] font-semibold">
            150+ <span class="text-[#b5aeff]"> Countries Reached</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#6b7280] mt-5">
            Our global footprint expands across continents.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="w-1/4 p-4">
          <h3 class="text-[#776bff] font-semibold">
            100% <span class="text-[#b5aeff]">Employee Growth</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#6b7280] mt-5">
            Doubling our team to double our impact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="w-1/4 p-4">
          <h3 class="text-[#776bff] font-semibold">
            10+ <span class="text-[#b5aeff]">Industry Awards</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#6b7280] mt-5">
            Recognition for innovation and excellence
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row p-5 my-5">
        <div class="col-6">
          <h1 class="font-semibold pb-3">Explore Our Current Openings</h1>
          <p>
            Ready to make your mark? Take a look at our exciting job
            opportunities.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="px-4">
            <span
              class="mb-4 inline-block bg-purple-100 text-[#776bff] text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide px-2 py-1 rounded"
            >
              Analytics Department
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2.5 leading-7 text-[#111928]">
              Senior Data Analyst
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-2.5 mt-0">December 21, 2023</p>
            <p class="text-base mt-0 mb-1 text-gray-500 font-medium">
              Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are
              becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both
              web designers and developers influence both web designers and
              developers.
            </p>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="text-[#776bff] font-semibold text-base font-medium inline-flex items-center mt-4 hover:text-[#443ab9] mb-8"
              style="font-size: 18px;"
            >
              Read more →
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2.5 leading-7 text-[#111928]">
              Wearable Tech in Advertising: Charting the Course of Immersive
              Marketing
            </h2>
            <span
              class="mb-8 inline-block bg-purple-100 text-[#776bff] text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide px-2 py-1 rounded"
            >
              Updates
            </span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-2.5 mt-0">December 21, 2023</p>
            <p class="text-base mt-0 mb-2.5 text-gray-500 font-medium">
              In the dynamic world of technology and advertising, wearable tech
              is emerging as a frontier brimming with innovative opportunities.
              As an expert in tech gadgets and their intersection with
              advertising, I am excited to delve into how wearable technology is
              not…
            </p>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="text-[#776bff] font-semibold text-base font-medium inline-flex items-center mt-4 hover:text-[#443ab9] mb-8"
              style="font-size: 18px;"
            >
              Read more →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <CompanyCultureSection />
</Base>
